Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A healthy soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...resides in a healthy mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and in a healthy body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Sid-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:32.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to save Shinigami-sama, too, if possible. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was too far away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:37.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is a mere excuse... Please forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:41.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You made the best choice under those circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:45.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a witch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it all comes down to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:57.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no technique that we can use against Soul Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:58.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kilik-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If Soul Protect is used, {\alpha&HFF&}we're helpless...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If Soul Protect is used, we're helpless...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:07.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Our battle with the witches has lasted for many centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:12.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When the witches create a new spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:17.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Technicians and weapons come up with new techniques in order to go up against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:24.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to track down the witches, Technicians with soul sensing techniques were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:28.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to prevent that they created "Soul Protect."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:31.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we must find another technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:35.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's left is to turn into a Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn into a Kishin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this I guess there's no point in hiding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:47.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If we cover everything that reeks, we won't know what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:54.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There comes a time when we must remove the lid, and tell the kids what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gather around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:05.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Kishin below Shibusen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Don't you think that's a bit too straight forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:55.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened before Shibusen was established.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:01.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of a man known as Ashura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashura would wrap a long muffler around his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and wear five or six shirts over each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:14.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He refused to trust people or trust his heart to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:19.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He was like a pile of suspicions in a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation on those damn witches of the eastern area?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When we arrived there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...all of them were already slain by Ashura himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Among my direct special force,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:38.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Eight Powerful Shinigami Warriors, Ashura was by far the strongest person there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was always scared of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,An ultimate wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:49.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He became attached to power, and eventually he broke the rule,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:52.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he started consuming human souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the beginning of madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Birth of Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:14.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But souls are something that only weapons can eat right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How was he able to eat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:21.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also scared senseless of his partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he ate all of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:29.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:34.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...he might not have been a human to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:40.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What lay deep in his heart, where one's eyes can't reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...was something like fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Underground Battle Starts:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakthrough, Medusa's Vector Arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:54.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kid-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:58.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Shinigami-sama seal Ashura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Father removed Ashura's skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:05.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He sealed him with a seal made from that skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:10.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He rooted his soul and body here to prevent the Kishin from awakening...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the Shinigami master can't get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:17.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the seal is broken and he gets away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Shinigami-sama be able to move freely again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, Shinigami-sama fixed his soul to this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and became one with Death City.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,One with Death City...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:34.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to be able to move, this city would have to grow out legs in order to move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's just impossible to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:43.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The consequences of Kishin's revival are far greater than we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Madness is contagious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:02.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul... you can't hold it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell is up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:08.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,One's heart is a fragile thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Madness awaits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:18.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the needle running in the groove of the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your persuasive power is so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That needle there is jumping around like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for your decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen's anniversary party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:52.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blair wanted to go too, but they said only Shibusen students are allowed to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:58.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have work today, and I don't the have money to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:04.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can see his intentions, I guess I'll go stop by the fish store that gives me goodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:11.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}Blair-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Blair-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fish Seller?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,H-{\alpha&HFF&}Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:20.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you this fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fish Seller!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what you did to the bait I finally found.\NHow are you going to repay me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Impertinent little rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been running for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:01.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Maka, do you feel any witch's soul response up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they're hiding it with Protect now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, how boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:09.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's your one and only strong point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You really piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:17.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Right ahead of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a soul response from behind the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This obscene and horrible sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Obscene and horrible sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty amazing that you were able to get out of that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:46.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm known to be the fastest one to chase a woman's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about how far I could go without a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:07.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on there's no telling what could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The weapons must not return to their human form no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance that a single attack may take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.18,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They're waiting ahead of this?{\alpha&HFF&} Aren't they headed to the Kishin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They're waiting ahead of this? Aren't they headed to the Kishin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they shouldn't all be headed there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, can't you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like they're finally coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,One who's confident of not being ganged up on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:53.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...when there is more than one enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:58.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And is also able to attack and hold back those few enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would be you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:21.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give you guys a little plan of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can somewhat predict this plan of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one to prevent us from going on is Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you pass her there's the second obstacle, the Devil Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:38.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And the remaining two should be heading toward the Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The werewolf Maka met before should be using...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...his immortal body guarding the black blood by all means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So for the moves that we will be making...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,First I will take care of Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:56.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you pass Medusa as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:12:00.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all of us, the one with the most mobility is Kid-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:03.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be going after the two heading toward the Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:09.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star's job is to hold down the Devil Sword so Kid and Maka can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:14.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're good at pounding soul waves, you're the only one who can damage her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:20.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pass both Medusa and the Evil Sword, catch up with Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:22.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and together, stop the Black Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:32.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A strategy meeting right in front of the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you're Shibusen's nurse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You wise guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nake, Snake, Cobra, Cobabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nake, Snake, Cobra, Cobabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen, you don't have to try and all go at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:12:59.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,An opening will definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush it, keep calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Great calculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good magic to hold back a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus its power is stronger than the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz, if you're scared, go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, Demon Blade mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Impertinent kids are to be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.32,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka, Black Star, I'll be going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:42.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:49.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them got through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Demon Blade mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka, let's follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,All vectors to Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the movement of this magic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My path was decided from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Going through the center!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Arrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...fly out from Medusa and make a circular movement inward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a way through them then the middle is the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:24.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But the center is also where one will feel the arrows' pressure the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a small hesitation could mean losing your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:31.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If one doesn't make it past them before the arrows gather, it's fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus only on running!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerate to my fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting your sense of vision to overcome the fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:47.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrows' sounds are getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:50.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, the worst case scenario is being created.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs feel so heavy because I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:05.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's why I can give it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't this interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent is none but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What a miscalculation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think all three would pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:47.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as I've held you, Stein, this plan is a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the three of the go there, it won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off not underestimating them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:58.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been observing at Shibusen until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Youngster...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Sword awaits them in the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:13.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:18.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Did something just pass by here really fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you in your infirmary uniform made my heart beat fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:29.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was the only one who was going to remove that uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with her though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching, damn it! You got a head start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep fooling around in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With that expression of yours, I'll dance with you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately that's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...not with those feet of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet, when did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Sewing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:07.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When that Soul Purge hit you before, I used my soul frequency...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...and left something like an electric charge on your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:17.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I controlled it like a string and sewed your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to precisely control your soul that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:25.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The weapon's effect on the technician's soul isn't merely amplification...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:28.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It can improve precise control over the soul too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:32.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A technique that is possible because of the best technician and weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:36.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa, I'll say this at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only Death Scythe in Shibusen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If I allow the rebirth of the Kishin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't be able to face the other Death Scythes around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:52.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're definitely going to win is what you want to say, right, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein! Don't steal my finishing lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're history!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.80,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're headed is not this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:15.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:22.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever stands on that plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...is blown in the direction it's pointing to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:33.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And, of course, it has an effect on me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:43.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of close combat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:46.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, make your way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:49.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He sewed his own body down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But under what circumstances can you avoid this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Removal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:06.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Finding the right timing, and using the plate as a counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:13.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:20.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a thousand snakes inside my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't let a prey that comes close escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:26.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the "afraid of close combat" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, after all, a short ranged witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Infiltrating as an infirmary nurse...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:39.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,"Won't you come with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said during the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are interested in the world I desire too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Franken Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you as a Shibusen teacher. I'm asking you as a researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, what's wrong Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrows around you aim towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:15.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I always obtain what I desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:24.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... I already let someone pass by easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get scolded again. I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Devil Sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:36.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like I'll be able to stand out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be on something, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I really don't give a damn about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is how I'm going to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.94,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Black Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Black Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here faster than I thought for a slowpoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:03.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:07.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:13.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But Maka-chan, in Professor's plan, Black Star is to take care of the Devil Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Our attacks won't have any effect on the Devil Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:20.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, don't mess with my stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, missie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to get carried away, I'll kill you, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:40.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The honor student Maka, disobeying a teacher's order, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.34,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Reached the rebellious age?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll make this stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...yours to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible, because there's no more material left! It's definitely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying Yamatoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:26.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:28.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...we won't treat you badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just like Minami-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:31.92,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's doing their best...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:33.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you do your best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what the director said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boss, you say something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:39.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It is for the show, so stop whining and give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:44.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I swung around the scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I spoke in front of 1000 people for an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew the picture in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:50.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I didn't get any sleep after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:52.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyhow, I'll be treated as a backstabber either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Backstabbers can only work in the back. I'm already doing so!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:58.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The late show crew treats me like a part timer too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who doesn't have a choice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.47,0:24:02.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Don't you think this is about ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:06.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it looks good. Okay then, boss give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:07.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What, me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:08.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:10.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else is going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:11.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not good with these kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:14.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess up, I'll punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess up, I'll break your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:17.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess up, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:18.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with all the pressure on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:23.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:24.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:25.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
